Package: workflowr
Type: Package
Title: A workflow template for creating a research website
Version: 0.3.0
Author: John Blischak
Maintainer: John Blischak <jdblischak@uchicago.edu>
Description: workflowr provides helper functions to get started using R Markdown
    to create a research website.
